                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17980912-59-defend614 t17980912-59-punish352"></join>
               Transported for seven years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice ROOKE.</p>
